1. Install Arduino IDE from https://www.arduino.cc/en/software
2. In Arduino IDE add Controllino Board
  > Tools/Boards Manager
    > Add Controllino 3.1.0 board
3. In Arduino IDE add libraries
  > Tools/ Manage Libraries 
    > Add RingBuf 2.0.0
    > Add SPI (should be automatically included)
    > Add Ethernet (should be automatically included)
    > Add PubSubClient 2.8.0
 4. In Arduino IDE add custom library
    > Scatch/ Include Library / Add ZIP Library
      > Pull LanceControllino from GIT and pack it to ZIP file
      > Add Library
 5. Open INO files in Arduino IDE and update controllino boxes.
 
 LanceHomeModule 1
 LanceHomeModule 2
 
